Title: MUSHROOM 11
Genre: Action - Adventure - Puzzle
Works on: Windows (XP, Vista, 7, 8, 10), Mac OS X (10.7+) and Linux (Ubuntu 14.04, Mint 17)
Languages: Text only: English
Modes: Single-player
Released: October 15, 2015
Size: 180.9 MB
Company: Untame / Untame
Rating: SRB Rating: Everyone 10+ (with Fantasy Violence, Mild Blood)
Store page: http://www.gog.com/game/mushroom_11

About:
Mold an amorphous organism into any shape by pruning its cells. New cells will immediately grow, allowing you to traverse a mysterious world across brain-twisting obstacles, overcome swarms of bizarre mutated creatures, and understand the true nature of the devastation from which you emerged.
Mold breaking game about destruction and growth!
7 Chapters each with a changing enviorment!
Music by The Future Sound of London

Minimum system requirements - Windows: XP / Vista / 7 / 8 / 10
Memory: 2 GB RAM
Hard Drive: 500 MB available space
